data.revised_prompt: Create an icon that symbolically represents the '1666 Great Fire of London' set against a pure white backdrop. The icon should integrate easily identifiable forms such as stylized flames, an abstract rendition of St. Paul's Cathedral, and iconic architectural elements associated with London. The design should also sustain clear visuals and effective impact even when reduced to petite dimensions. Employ a color palette that is striking and contrast-filled to highlight the themes of fire and devastation.
